WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
Welcome to the Ocean Ecology Documentary

00:05.000 --> 00:10.000
This is a fascinating look at marine biodiversity

00:10.000 --> 00:15.000
The ocean covers seventy percent of the Earth's surface

00:15.000 --> 00:20.000
Millions of species live beneath the waves

00:20.000 --> 00:25.000
Let's explore this mysterious world together

00:25.000 --> 00:30.000
The deep sea has unique ecosystems

00:30.000 --> 00:35.000
Many species remain undiscovered by humans

00:35.000 --> 00:40.000
Protecting marine ecology is our shared responsibility

00:40.000 --> 00:46.000
Thank you for watching. Let's protect our blue planet
